pha.com/article/4741457-aptargroup-has-gotten-too-expensive", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 13:28:39"}, {"id": "4741456", "title": "URA: Nuclear's Rebound Has Legs, Bullish Heading Into 2025", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1991625088/image_1991625088.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Distribution Warehouse Interior With Radioactive Waste Barrels On Racks\" data-id=\"1991625088\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1991625088/image_1991625088.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1991625088/image_1991625088.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1991625088/image_1991625088.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1991625088/image_1991625088.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1991625088/image_1991625088.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1991625088/image_1991625088.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1991625088/image_1991625088.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1991625088/image_1991625088.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">onurdongel</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>It has been a volatile year for investors in the Global X Uranium ETF (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSEARCA:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/URA\" title=\"Global X Uranium ETF\">URA</a></span>). Shares surged from under $20 in the middle of 2023 to above $33 by this past June. A steep correction ensued in the third quarter, bringing the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1991625088/image_1991625088.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741456-ura-etf-nuclear-rebound-has-legs-bullish-heading-into-2025", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 13:21:17"}, {"id": "4741438", "title": "HP Inc.: Buy The Dip And Wait For AI Wave To Drive PC Rebound", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/495561838/image_495561838.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Hewlett Packard 650BK ink for a ink jet printer\" data-id=\"495561838\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1017px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/495561838/image_495561838.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/495561838/image_495561838.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/495561838/image_495561838.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/495561838/image_495561838.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/495561838/image_495561838.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/495561838/image_495561838.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/495561838/image_495561838.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/495561838/image_495561838.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Dejan-Deko/iStock Editorial via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Value stocks are hard to come by in today's market, with the post-Trump election rally fueling higher multiples across basically every industry. I'm still holding on to the macro view, however, that markets are bound for a 10-20% correction</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/495561838/image_495561838.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741438-hp-inc-buy-the-dip-and-wait-for-ai-wave-to-drive-pc-rebound", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 11:12:37"}, {"id": "4741443", "title": "Nutanix, Inc. 2025 Q1 - Results - Earnings Call Presentation", "description": "<p>The following slide deck was published by Nutanix, Inc. in conjunction with their 2025 Q1 earnings call.</p> <p><figure class=\"sa-presentation paywall-full-content invisible\" data-id=\"105988\"></figure></p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741443-nutanix-inc-2025-q1-results-earnings-call-presentation", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 10:53:15"}, {"id": "4741436", "title": "Pizza Pizza Royalty: A Slice Of Dividends And A Little Bit More", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1865411614/image_1865411614.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Preparando Broccoli Crust Pepperoni Pizza\" data-id=\"1865411614\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1865411614/image_1865411614.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1865411614/image_1865411614.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1865411614/image_1865411614.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1865411614/image_1865411614.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static